-- site-doc.header: How to create a business card using fastn

This guide is for anyone who wants to create their own business card from
scratch. 

This entirely runs on the browser. Simply follow along the steps to get 
started.



-- ftd.desktop:

-- ftd.column:
width: fill-container

-- tf.h3: `Step 1`: Sign Up or Sign In on GitHub

- [Sign Up](https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%2F&source=header-home)
  on GitHub if you do not have a GitHub account already, else 
  [Sign In](https://github.com/login) 
  to your GitHub account.

  [Read about GitHub](https://fastn.com/book/github/)


-- ftd.column:
width: fill-container
align-content: left


