-- tf.h3: Improve the URL accessibility

You may wish to change your information in future, in that case to check the 
updates you will need to come to `Settings > Pages` everytime. 

Instead, you can access it from the `Code` tab itself. 

- Copy the URL of live site by going to `Settings > Pages`


-- ftd.image:
src: $assets.files.images.live-site-url.png
width.fixed.px: 750
border-radius.px: 10
border-width.px: 1
border-color: $inherited.colors.border
margin-vertical.px: 16


-- tf.markdown:

- Go to `Code` tab (first tab) 

- On the right side, you will find `About section`, click on the `Settings` 
icon (⚙️) 

- In the `Edit repository details` popup, paste the Website URL in the second 
field

- Click on `Save`


-- ftd.image:
src: $assets.files.images.about-section.png
width.fixed.px: 750
border-radius.px: 10
border-width.px: 1
border-color: $inherited.colors.border
margin-vertical.px: 16

-- tf.markdown:

Now you can access your website from `About` section.

